text: Val-de-Dagne is a commune of 739 people (2017). It is in Occitanie in the Aude department in south France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2019 and consists of the former communes of Montlaur and Pradelles-en-Val.Arrêté préfectoral 5 December 2018 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Aude
title: Val-de-Dagne
